OL,3,CBBC bosses to be questioned by MPs
OL,4,Camid Gaza documentary controversy
OL,6,FThe BBC director general and chairman
OL,7,Fare to appear before the Culture,
OL,8,FMedia and Sport Committee amid the
OL,9,Fcorporation facing a backlash over a
OL,10,Fdocumentary on Gaza which featured the
OL,11,Fson of a Hamas official.
OL,13,FThe session with Tim Davie and Samir
OL,14,FShah on Tuesday morning was already
OL,15,Fscheduled as part of the committee's
OL,16,Fongoing scrutiny into the work of the
OL,17,Fcorporation.
