OL,3,CBBC bosses to be questioned by MPs
OL,4,Camid Gaza documentary controversy
OL,6,FIt is expected that the BBC bosses
OL,7,Fwill be asked about a range of issues
OL,8,Fincluding editorial processes and
OL,9,Fimpartiality, according to the session
OL,10,Foutline.
OL,12,FMr Davie and Dr Shah will also likely
OL,13,Fbe questioned on workplace culture,
OL,14,Fthe future of TV distribution and the
OL,15,Frole and regulation of public service
OL,16,Fbroadcasters.
