OL,6,FFunding and the financial challenges
OL,7,Ffaced by the BBC ahead of the review
OL,8,Fof its charter, which is due to expire
OL,9,Fat the end of 2027, will also likely
OL,10,Fbe discussed.
OL,12,FIt comes amid the broadcaster
OL,13,Fapologising last week for "serious
OL,14,Fflaws" in the making of the programme
OL,15,FGaza: How To Survive A Warzone.
