OL,3,CBBC bosses to be questioned by MPs
OL,4,Camid Gaza documentary controversy
OL,6,FThe corporation removed the
OL,7,Fdocumentary from BBC iPlayer after it
OL,8,Femerged that the child narrator is the
OL,9,Fson of Ayman Alyazouri, who has worked
OL,10,Fas Hamas's deputy minister of
OL,11,Fagriculture.
OL,13,FAfter conducting an initial review of
OL,14,Fthe programme, the broadcaster said
OL,15,Findependent production company Hoyo
OL,16,FFilms, who made the documentary, told
OL,17,Fthem the boy's mother had been paid "a
OL,18,Flimited sum of money for the
OL,19,Fnarration".
OL,26,@yD@eOU{D@JO]
