OL,3,CBBC bosses to be questioned by MPs
OL,4,Camid Gaza documentary controversy
OL,6,FThe BBC added that it has no plans to
OL,7,Fbroadcast the documentary again or
OL,8,Freturn it to iPlayer.
OL,10,FIn a letter to the BBC on Monday,
OL,11,FOfcom chairman Lord Grade said the
OL,12,Fregulator could step in if an internal
OL,13,Finquiry into the making of the
OL,14,Fdocumentary is not satisfactory.
OL,16,FLord Grade said Ofcom has "ongoing
OL,17,Fconcerns about the nature and gravity
OL,18,Fof these failings and the negative
OL,19,Fimpact they have on the trust
OL,20,Faudiences place in the BBC's
OL,21,Fjournalism".
