OL,6,FHe added: "We will continue to keep
OL,7,Fthe situation under close review and
OL,8,Fwill expect regular updates from the
OL,9,FBBC regarding both timeframes and
OL,10,Fprogress and reserve the right to use
OL,11,Four powers to step in should we feel
OL,12,Fit necessary to do so, given that the
OL,13,FBBC Board has decided these to be
OL,14,Finternal investigations."
