OL,3,CBBC bosses to be questioned by MPs
OL,4,Camid Gaza documentary controversy
OL,6,FOver the weekend, the Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice said it had received a "number
OL,8,Fof reports raising concerns" and that
OL,9,Fofficers from its Counter Terrorism
OL,10,FCommand are "assessing whether any
OL,11,Fpolice action is required in relation
OL,12,Fto this matter".
OL,14,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy also met
OL,15,Fthe BBC chairman on Friday after
OL,16,Fsaying she wanted assurances "that no
OL,17,Fstone will be left unturned" during a
OL,18,Freview into the documentary.
