OL,6,FAfter conducting the initial review, a
OL,7,FBBC spokesperson said last week that
OL,8,F"serious flaws in the making of this
OL,9,Fprogramme" had been identified.
OL,11,FThey added: "Some of these were made
OL,12,Fby the production company and some by
OL,13,Fthe BBC; all of them are unacceptable.
OL,15,F"BBC News takes full responsibility
OL,16,Ffor these and the impact that these
OL,17,Fhave had on the corporation's
OL,18,Freputation. We apologise for this.
