OL,6,F"Nothing is more important than the
OL,7,Ftrust that our audiences have in our
OL,8,Fjournalism. This incident has damaged
OL,9,Fthat trust.
OL,11,F"While the intent of the documentary
OL,12,Fwas aligned with our purpose ` to tell
OL,13,Fthe story of what is happening around
OL,14,Fthe world, even in the most difficult
OL,15,Fand dangerous places ` the processes
OL,16,Fand execution of this programme fell
OL,17,Fshort of our expectations.
