OL,6,F"Although the programme was made by an
OL,7,Findependent production company, who
OL,8,Fwere commissioned to deliver a fully
OL,9,Fcompliant documentary, the BBC has
OL,10,Fultimate editorial responsibility for
OL,11,Fthis programme as broadcast."
OL,13,FLast week, protesters gathered outside
OL,14,FBroadcasting House in London claiming
OL,15,Fthe BBC had aired Hamas propaganda.
