OL,6,FThe BBC also faced criticism for
OL,7,Fpulling the documentary, with Gary
OL,8,FLineker, Anita Rani, Riz Ahmed and
OL,9,FMiriam Margolyes among more than 500
OL,10,Fmedia figures who had condemned the
OL,11,Faction.
OL,13,FIn an open letter addressed to Mr
OL,14,FDavie, chairman Dr Shah and outgoing
OL,15,Fchief content officer Charlotte Moore,
OL,16,Fhundreds of TV and film professionals
OL,17,Fand journalists called the decision to
OL,18,Fremove the documentary "politically
OL,19,Fmotivated censorship".
